Fee Income and Other
2015 vs. 2014: The decrease compared to the same period of 2014 in net fee income and other expenses was driven by decreased engineering fee income within EPC, plus Specialty discontinued lines.
2014 vs. 2013: The decrease in net fee income and other was driven by increased costs in our risk engineering services business.
